channel.title: Project Runescape 718 with 745 cache
channel.description:
Welcome to Project Runescape
Forums: http://projectrs.netii.net/forums/
Download .zip: https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/73757294/DevastationX/Project%20Runescape.zip
Download .jar: https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/73757294/ProjectRunescape.jar
Cache Stuff
Fixed all the maps Solved tons of nulls all over the place and with items
Fixed the sprites, added in fun crowns and interfaces for people to use
No more black screen, cache loads instantly on first login
Some cool custom items
Features
Prestige system
Slave system
Duel arena
Dominion tower (no rewards yet)
Castle wars
Unique home&training zone
Clue scrolls
Quests
Crystal chest with good rewards Working fairy rings Trivia
